:180},"两千年前的埃拉托色尼如何求解地球周长？",{"type":167,"tag":168,"props":182,"children":183},{},[184],{"type":172,"value":185},"塞伊尼是一个著名的景点，位于被回归线上，其中有一口井会在太阳的照射下不产生阴影。埃拉托色尼选取了和塞伊尼同经线的亚历山大的一座尖塔，并根据同一天正午的尖塔高度及其阴影长度，计算出了太阳在亚历山大的高度角。再加上他打听到的塞伊尼与亚历山大的直线距离，算出了地球的周长，约为四万公里，很接近现代测量结果。",{"type":167,"tag":168,"props":187,"children":188},{},[189],{"type":167,"tag":190,"props":191,"children":194},"img",{"alt":192,"src":193},"求解示意","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20220117233422.png",[],{"type":167,"tag":196,"props":197,"children":199},"h2",{"id":198},"references",[200],{"type":172,"value":201},"References",{"type":167,"tag":203,"props":204,"children":205},"ul",{},[206,219],{"type":167,"tag":207,"props":208,"children":209},"li",{},[210],{"type":167,"tag":211,"props":212,"children":216},"a",{"href":213,"rel":214},"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Ma4y1e7rx",[215],"nofollow",[217],{"type":172,"value":218},"古埃及人是怎么早在2200多年前就测量出地球周长的？",{"type":167,"tag":207,"props":220,"children":221},{},[222],{"type":167,"tag":211,"props":223,"children":226},{"href":224,"rel":225},"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1GJ41197eB",[215],[227],{"type":172,"value":228},"伪史批判：造假的古希腊天文和地理学",{"title":160,"searchDepth":230,"depth":230,"links":231},2,[232],{"id":198,"depth":230,"text":201},"markdown","content:6.maps:_person:eratosthenes.md","content","6.maps/_person/eratosthenes.md","6.maps/_person/eratosthenes","md",[240,244],{"_path":241,"title":242,"description":243},"/maps/_person/claudius-ptolemaeus","克罗狄斯·托勒密","地心说",{"_path":245,"title":246,"description":247},"/maps/_person/henry-molaison","亨利·莫莱森","医学史上最著名的健忘症患者",1742745252587]